item.title: CVE-2021-1246|2024-08-03T16:02:56.385Z -- cisco -- cisco%20finesse
item.description: Multiple vulnerabilities in the web-based management interface of Cisco Finesse could allow an unauthenticated, remote attacker to conduct a cross-site scripting (XSS) attack and obtain potentially confidential information by leveraging a flaw in the authentication mechanism. For more information about these vulnerabilities, see the Details section of this advisory.
